Proposed (77.7s): Use when the user is working on a **Wonder site** — a project built from `wonder-image/new-site` or whose `composer.json` depends on `wonder-image/app`. Trigger whenever the query involves: adding or editing pages/components (`custom/view/`), locale files or translations (`lang/`, `pages.json`, `__t()`), URL helpers (`__r()`, `__u()`), Wonder lib CSS classes (`wi-btn-*`, `wi-card-*`, `wi-form-*`, `wi-modal-*`), activating or debugging a `wonder-image/<slug>` Composer module, site Models/Resources in `app/`, or permissions in `custom/config/`. Applies to queries in Italian or any language. Skip when editing `vendor/wonder-image/app` internals (use wi-app instead).

